OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine once again, with
OL,6,Ffurther sunshine for a time, perhaps
OL,7,Fhazy under high cloud. Still hot but
OL,8,Fmarkedly less so than Friday. Further
OL,9,Fshowers and thunderstorms are possible
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear skies at first becoming
OL,13,Fcloudy by the morning with the chance
OL,14,Fof some light rain moving in from the
OL,15,Fwest during the early hours. Overnight
OL,16,Ftemperatures remaining very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
