OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,6,Fto all parts into Sunday, with rain at
OL,7,Ffirst then some sunny intervals during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. More seasonable
OL,9,Ftemperatures than expected. Winds
OL,10,Fmoderate southwesterly.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fis looking dry and settled. Turning
OL,14,Fmore unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,15,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,16,Fof sunny, then clouding over with
OL,17,Fpatchy rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
